data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value: Welcome to my social tolerance simulator! This program was designed to show how our tolerance of people different than us can affect or living and moving habits. To start the simulation, press "Start". You can look at a single move by pressing the "Step" button, or stop the simulation at any time. If you'd like to start the simulation again, press "Repopulate" to fill the board with a new population.
